{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_14061.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story08","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200501,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200701,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":200501}],"nameLeft":"Mami","nameRight":"Nagisa","textLeft":"I...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":200501}],"textLeft":"I made a very big mistake in this city."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200701}],"textRight":"Mistake..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200701,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"(Is this related to the \"big whatever-it-is\"@that happened here?)","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200501,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"I don't know if what I thought was right was@really right...","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":200501}],"textLeft":"Or if by doing the right thing, I have to@give up on everything I can't save..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":200501}],"textLeft":"It's so difficult... I have no idea what I@should do."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200501,"motion":400}],"textLeft":"Oh! I'm sorry. You have no idea what I'm@talking about."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200701,"motion":0}],"textRight":"It's fine! Go ahead and tell me!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200501,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"Okay."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"I... I wanted to fix the mistakes I made."},{"chara":[{"id":200501}],"textLeft":"I wanted to save the people I'd gotten@involved..."},{"chara":[{"id":200501}],"textLeft":"The people who were affected by the@whole situation."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200501,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"But in the end... I just made an even bigger@and much more serious mistake."},{"chara":[{"id":200501}],"textLeft":"I just wanted to save everyone, but I ended@up creating trouble for them."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200501}],"textLeft":"I was foolish... To tell you the truth, I @have no right to look them in the eye now."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"I don't know why..."},{"chara":[{"id":200501}],"textLeft":"I thought I'd moved on, but I still regret@everything I've done..."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"That's why I keep finding myself here."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200701,"motion":300}],"textRight":"I see..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200501,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"..."},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":200501,"motion":400}],"textBg":"shout","textLeft":"Ah, actually, on second thought, forget @everything I just said!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200501}],"textLeft":"What am I even saying to you, Nagisa..."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"Sorry!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200701,"motion":0}],"textRight":"Ahhh! You apologized again!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200501}],"textLeft":"Oh..."},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime03","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200701,"motion":100}],"textRight":"Haha!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200501}],"textLeft":"I did, didn't I?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200501,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"Then I'll treat you to ice cream!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200701}],"textRight":"Really? [chara:200701:lipSynch_0][wait:0.8][chara:200701:motion_200][chara:200701:effect_emotion_joy_0][se:7222_happy][chara:200701:cheek_0][chara:200701:face_mtn_ex_011.exp.json][chara:200701:lipSynch_1]Yay!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200701}],"textRight":"I want cheese flavored!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200501}],"textLeft":"Cheese? So you like cheese."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200701,"motion":100}],"textRight":"[chara:200701:effect_emotion_joy_0][se:7222_happy]I sure do!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200501,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"Got it! Then let's go."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200701}],"textRight":"Let's!"},{"bgm":"stop","nameNarration":"Nagisa","narration":"We're making progress, little by little.@She's not going to open up all at once.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"But I knew it.@Something happened to Mami here...@There's no doubt about that."},{"narration":"So what was it that happened?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200701,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_04"}],"nameCenter":"Nagisa","textCenter":"I'm all worked up thinking about it. I'm@so worried...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"stop"},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":200701,"motion":0}]},{"chara":[{"id":200701}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}